    <h3>Winter</h3>
    <p>
      The meteorological definition of Winter according to SMHI is:
      "the period when the average daily temperature is 0.0 degrees or lower for five consecutive days".
      The winter can not occur before the 1st of August"
    </p>
    <p>This also never happens in our data, in this case, however, we have chosen not to modify the terms more than to try so that our method works, which it does.</p>
